Differences of male types (according to original description: 
Fischer 1966
). Fore wing length 4.4 mm. Mandible 1.3 times as long as its maximum width. Antenna 38-39-segmented. First flagellar segment 3.0 times as long as its apical width. Mesoscutum about as long as its maximum width. Hind femur 4.5 times as long as its maximum width.
